Stanley K. Bernstein is a Canadian physician who founded and is current owner of 60 weight-loss clinics in Canada and the United States, known collectively as the Dr. Bernstein Diet & Health Clinics. Bernstein has owned and operated weight-loss clinics for more than 35 years  and employs a weight-loss regimen involving a low calorie intake, frequent physician visits and injections of a Vitamin B solution. Bernstein is a member of the American Society of Bariatric Physicians.
